Type III CRISPR-Cas locus browser

This website is released as Supplementary Material for Hoikkala, Graham & White 2024 paper, currently in review.

  • Add filters by clicking "Add Condition".
  • Note that the table scrolls horizontally.
  • Hover your mouse over the figures to enlarge them
  • Columns and rows can be reordered
  • Download the (filtered) data by clicking Export to Excel.
